1335:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ForcedAction_Active: Force active level on OC2REF
1336:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ForcedAction_InActive: Force inactive level on OC2REF.
1337:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @retval None
