1379:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @brief  Forces the TIMx output 4 waveform to active or inactive level.
1380:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @param  TIMx: where x can be  1, 2, 3, 4, 5 or 8 to select the TIM peripheral.
