1382:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *   This parameter can be one of the following values:
1383:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ForcedAction_Active: Force active level on OC4REF
1384:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ForcedAction_InActive: Force inactive level on OC4REF.
