1573:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c **** /**
1574:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @brief  Enables or disables the TIMx peripheral Preload register on CCR4.
