1748:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c **** /**
1749:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @brief  Clears or safeguards the OCREF3 signal on an external event
