1938:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c **** /**
1939:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @brief  Configures the TIMx channel 4 polarity.
