2347:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ICPSC_DIV1: no prescaler
2348:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ICPSC_DIV2: capture is done once every 2 events
2349:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ICPSC_DIV4: capture is done once every 4 events
2350:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   *     @arg TIM_ICPSC_DIV8: capture is done once every 8 events
2351:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @retval None
