2519:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @param  TIMx: where x can be 1 to 17 to select the TIM peripheral.
2520:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   * @retval Prescaler Register value.
2521:../Libraries//STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_tim.c ****   */
